 <h1>CSS</h1>
<p>CSS stands for Cashcading Style Sheets.
    CSS is the language we use to style an HTML document.</p>
<p>Types of CSS:</p>
<ul style="list-style-type: upper-roman;"><li>Inline CSS</li>
<li>Internal CSS</li>
<li>External CSS</li></ul>
<p>By using CSS we control</p>
<ul style="list-style-type:upper-alpha;"><li>Color</li>
<li>Font</li>
<li>Size of the text</li>
<li>Spacing between the elements</li>
<li>Background-color</li>
<li>Background-images and etc.,</li>
</ul>
